first_rows.0: Export to JSON plugin for PHPMyAdmin

comment.mode: Export to JSON plugin for PHPMyAdmin

bar.name: Count
bar.caption: A simple visualization of nullity by column.

matrix.name: Matrix
matrix.caption: Nullity matrix is a data-dense display which lets you quickly visually pick out patterns in data completion.

heatmap.name: Heatmap
heatmap.caption: The correlation heatmap measures nullity correlation: how strongly the presence or absence of one variable affects the presence of another.

dendrogram.name: Dendrogram
dendrogram.caption: The dendrogram allows you to more fully correlate variable completion, revealing trends deeper than the pairwise ones visible in the correlation heatmap.

package.pandas_profiling_config:
title: Pandas Profiling Report
dataset:
    description: ''
    creator: ''
    author: ''
    copyright_holder: ''
    copyright_year: ''
    url: ''
variables:
    descriptions: {}
show_variable_description: yes
pool_size: 0
progress_bar: yes
vars:
    num:
        quantiles:
        - 0.05
        - 0.25
        - 0.5
        - 0.75
        - 0.95
        skewness_threshold: 20
        low_categorical_threshold: 5
        chi_squared_threshold: 0.999
    cat:
        length: yes
        characters: yes
        words: yes
        cardinality_threshold: 50
        n_obs: 5
        chi_squared_threshold: 0.999
        coerce_str_to_date: no
        redact: no
    bool:
        n_obs: 3
        mappings:
        - [t, f]
        - ['yes', 'no']
        - [y, n]
        - ['true', 'false']
    file:
        active: no
    image:
        active: no
        exif: yes
        hash: yes
    path:
        active: no
    url:
        active: no
sort: None
missing_diagrams:
    bar: yes
    matrix: yes
    heatmap: yes
    dendrogram: yes
correlations:
    pearson:
        calculate: yes
        warn_high_correlations: yes
        threshold: 0.9
    spearman:
        calculate: yes
        warn_high_correlations: no
        threshold: 0.9
    kendall:
        calculate: yes
        warn_high_correlations: no
        threshold: 0.9
    phi_k:
        calculate: yes
        warn_high_correlations: no
        threshold: 0.9
    cramers:
        calculate: yes
        warn_high_correlations: yes
        threshold: 0.9
interactions:
    targets: []
    continuous: yes
categorical_maximum_correlation_distinct: 100
plot:
    image_format: svg
    dpi: 800
    scatter_threshold: 1000
    correlation:
        cmap: RdBu
        bad: '#000000'
    missing:
        cmap: RdBu
        force_labels: yes
    pie:
        max_unique: 10
    histogram:
        x_axis_labels: yes
        bins: 50
        max_bins: 250
n_obs_unique: 5
n_extreme_obs: 5
n_freq_table_max: 10
memory_deep: no
duplicates:
    head: 10
samples:
    head: 10
    tail: 10
    random: 0
reject_variables: yes
notebook:
    iframe:
        height: 800px
        width: 100%
        attribute: srcdoc
html:
    minify_html: yes
    use_local_assets: yes
    inline: yes
    navbar_show: yes
    file_name: None
    style:
        theme: None
        logo: ''
        primary_color: '#337ab7'
        full_width: no
